videos.description: Quinton Rose takes advantage of a lazy pass and steals the ball for an uncontested dunk.
videos.headline: Rose's steal leads to wide-open flush for Temple

videos.description: Tony Carr penetrates then delivers a dime to Julian Moore for a slam.
videos.headline: Penn State's Moore throws down two-handed flush

videos.description: Josh Brown somehow gets free for what seems like an open layup but Lamar Stevens recovers and rejects the potential game-tying basket.
videos.headline: Stevens gets big-time block for Penn State
